==English==

===Verb===
'''to belch''' ('''belched''', '''belches''', '''belching''')
#Loudly or rudely expel gas from your stomache out of your mouth
#:''In Arabia my friend, it is considered a compliment to the chef to '''belch''' after a fine meal.''

====Synonyms====
*[[burp]]

====See also====
*[[fart]] or [[pass gas]]
*[[expel]]

